<p><a name="footnote1" id="footnote1">1.</a> Alas, <tt>CPAN </tt>doesn't install the specified version of a module, so it is not possible to exactly replicate an environment bug-for-bug/feature-for-feature with <tt>Bundle</tt>s.</p>
